trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> event is raised by the designer host for certain actions on a control in the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>denne hendelsen oppstår ved designer verten for visse handlinger etter en kontroll i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>

trans-unit.source: For example, an event is raised when the user enters or exits template editing mode for a control.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel oppstår en hendelsen når brukeren skriver inn eller ut malen modus for en kontroll for redigering.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner> class supplies a default delegate to handle the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> event.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>klassen gir standard representant til å håndtere den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IControlDesignerView.ViewEvent> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Classes deriving from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner> override the OnTemplateModeChanged method to process events that are raised when the template mode changes for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Klasser som er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>Overstyr OnTemplateModeChanged-metoden på tjenesten hendelser som aktiveres når malen modusen endres for den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The OnTemplateModeChanged method allows derived classes to handle the event without attaching a delegate.
trans-unit.target: OnTemplateModeChanged metoden gjør det avledede klasser behandle hendelsen uten å knytte representant.

trans-unit.source: This is the preferred technique for handling the event in a derived class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er den foretrukne metoden for behandling av hendelsen i en avledet klasse.

trans-unit.source: The default delegate performs the updates that are required for a template mode change event in the base <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner> class, and then calls the OnTemplateModeChanged method.
trans-unit.target: Standard representanten utfører oppdateringer som kreves for en mal modus statusendringshendelsen i grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>klasse, og kaller deretter metoden OnTemplateModeChanged.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The base OnTemplateModeChanged method in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner> class returns without performing any additional processing for the event.
trans-unit.target: Grunnleggende OnTemplateModeChanged-metoden i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>klassen returnerer uten å utføre noen ytterligere behandling for hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: If a class derives from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner> and overrides the base OnTemplateModeChanged method, the default delegate calls the override method in the derived class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en klasse som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>og overstyringer base OnTemplateModeChanged metoden standard representanten kaller override-metoden i den utledede klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplatedControlDesigner>

trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InTemplateMode%2A>til å fastslå om kontrollen designer er i malen redigeringsmodus for øyeblikket.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.InTemplateMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: You should call this method to refresh the design-time display if the template frames have been changed without calling methods that update the design-time HTML automatically.
trans-unit.target: Du må kalle denne metoden for å oppdatere visningen utformingen hvis malen forhandleren har blitt endret uten å kalle metoder som automatisk Oppdater utformingen HTML.
